"Narrated Abu Musa:The Prophet (ﷺ) asked for some water and performed the ablution, and then raised his hands (towards the sky) and said, \"O Allah! Forgive `Ubaid Abi 'Amir.\" I saw the whiteness of his armpits (while he was raising his hands) and he added, \"O Allah! Upgrade him over many of Your human creatures on the Day of Resurrection"